OL,3,CGuernsey States told to introduce
OL,4,Cspeed cameras and penalty points
OL,6,FSpeed cameras and penalty points could
OL,7,Fbe introduced in Guernsey, in an
OL,8,Fattempt to crack down on dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FIt comes as the new Environment and
OL,12,FInfrastructure Committee looks to
OL,13,Fprioritise improving road safety, with
OL,14,Fthe support of the Home Affairs
OL,15,FCommittee.
OL,17,FSeveral recommendations for change
OL,18,Fhave been revealed in a report
OL,19,Fpublished by global infrastructure
OL,20,Fcompany AECOM - which cost the States
OL,21,Fmore than #55,000 to commission.
