OL,3,CGuernsey States told to introduce
OL,4,Cspeed cameras and penalty points
OL,6,FThe two committees say the rest of the
OL,7,Frecommendations "will be considered
OL,8,Falongside their other areas of
OL,9,Fbusiness and priorities".
OL,11,FOne of the suggestions not yet
OL,12,Factioned is introducing fixed speed
OL,13,Fcameras, which the report states could
OL,14,Fbe "placed at strategic points on the
OL,15,FGuernsey road network, such as
OL,16,Fjunctions, schools, and speeding
OL,17,Fhotspots".
