OL,3,CGuernsey States told to introduce
OL,4,Cspeed cameras and penalty points
OL,6,FAECOM add that the devices create "a
OL,7,Freal opportunity to reduce the risk of
OL,8,Faccidents, injuries, and fatalities on
OL,9,Fthe roads, as a consequence of
OL,10,Fspeeding".
OL,12,FThey say: "The benefits of the
OL,13,Fdifferent speed enforcement
OL,14,Ftechnologies vary but fundamentally
OL,15,Fprovide a 24/7 presence and deterrent,
OL,16,Frelatively low maintenance costs,
OL,17,Fautomatic detection and data sharing."
