OL,6,F"Everyone's conforming around that
OL,7,Fcamera but then off they go down the
OL,8,Froad, where they know there's no
OL,9,Fcameras.
OL,11,F"So one of the recommendations was
OL,12,Ffixed speed cameras, another one was
OL,13,Fmobile speed cameras."
